🚀 When Backend Sends a Notification
-------------------------------------

Once the token is stored, the sending path looks like this:

Backend
   │
   │ send notification using FCM token
   ▼
Firebase Cloud Messaging
   │
   │ routes message to APNs
   ▼
Apple Push Notification Service
   │
   ▼
iPhone Device
   │
   ▼
Notification Appears


