🧠 Key Insight (Important for Your Bug)
----------------------------------------

The listener is critical because this step can be delayed:
    --------

Firebase SDK
     │
     │ sends APNs token to Firebase
     ▼
Firebase generates FCM token

Sometimes this takes a few seconds.

If the app only does:

getToken()

once and the token is not ready → you get null → registration fails.

That’s why the correct approach is:

Start listener
Wait until token arrives
Then register device


