Where to get the Listner ?
---------------------------

Listener is not something you download or create yourself. 
You don’t get it anywhere — it is already provided by the plugin installed.

This import -
import { FirebaseMessaging } from "@capacitor-firebase/messaging";

That package already contains the listener implementation.
You only subscribe to it.


Think of it like this:
Capacitor Firebase Messaging Plugin
        │
        │ exposes events
        ▼
FirebaseMessaging.addListener(...)


Where It Comes From
--------------------
It comes from this npm package:
@capacitor-firebase/messaging



